<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4747414>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Onthophagus nyctopus. (a, b) Dorsal habitus of male and female. (c, d) Dorsal habitus of the lectotype and original labels (scale bar: 1 mm). (i, j) Lateral and dorsal view of the parameres (scale bar: 0.05 mm). (k, l) Lamella copulatrix and accessory lamellae; arrow indicating the basolateral carina of the inferior left lobe of O. nyctopus. (m) Female genitalia (scale bar: 0.02 mm). Onthophagus steinheili. (e, f) Dorsal habitus of male and female. (g, h) Dorsal habitus of the lectotype and original labels (scale bar: 1 mm). (n, o) Lateral and dorsal view of the parameres (scale bar: 0.05 mm). (p, q) Lamella copulatrix and accessory lamellae. (r) Female genitalia (scale bar: 0.02 mm)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4747414/files/figure.png" .

